Title: Preserves ecological integrity, wildlife and open space in the Adirondack park
Summary: Preserves ecological integrity, wildlife and open space in the Adirondack park; strengthens land use and development provisions in the Adirondack park so as to curtail rural sprawl.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the executive law, in relation to preserving ecological integrity, wildlife and open space in the Adirondack park
